    <title>Unity学习002-根据Brackeys佬教程实现门的场景转换</title>
    <url>/2021/09/13/Unity%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0002-%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AEBrackeys%E4%BD%AC%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>纯日志，无教程</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<p>参考视频：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CE9VOZivb3I">How to make AWESOME Scene Transitions in Unity!</a></p>
<h2 id="场景转换"><a href="#场景转换" class="headerlink" title="场景转换"></a>场景转换</h2><figure class="highlight c#"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">LoadNextScene</span>(<span class="params"></span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    StartCoroutine(LoadScene(sceneIndex));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">IEnumerator <span class="title">LoadScene</span>(<span class="params"><span class="built_in">int</span> sceneIndex</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//Play animation</span></span><br><span class="line">    transition.SetTrigger(<span class="string">&quot;Start&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//Wait animation</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">yield</span> <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title">WaitForSeconds</span>(<span class="params">transitionTime</span>)</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//Load</span></span><br><span class="line">    SceneManager.LoadSceneAsync(sceneIndex);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="门"><a href="#门" class="headerlink" title="门"></a>门</h2><p>门分为出去和进入两种，前者不需要进行输入，只进行接触判断；后者需要在接触判断时获得对应输入。</p>
]]></content>
